				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/%C4%90%E1%BB%99c-d%E1%BA%A1-khi%E1%BB%83n-ho%C3%A0i/poem-ErznbiboGRfla9sPRI_AFw">Độc dạ khiển hoài - 獨夜遣懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Thu%E1%BB%B5-Chi/M%E1%BA%ADu-Th%C3%ACn-xu%C3%A2n-du-Long-%C4%90%E1%BB%99i-s%C6%A1n-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-vFyLNHjIdIKOd6KEZSeY-w">Mậu Thìn xuân du Long Đội sơn tự - 戊辰春遊龍隊山寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Thu%E1%BB%B5-Chi/author-Ya8ICdCs1Ab5sFLe9rk-Pw">Hoàng Thuỵ Chi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/M%E1%BB%99c-Lan-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-6sfuvKunKe6MYqxIDetwJA">Mộc Lan từ - 木蘭詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Hwang-Jin-i/Ph%C3%A1c-Uy%C3%AAn/poem-aKuBcxAj85ypLiV_4ndxEg">Phác Uyên - 朴淵</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Hwang-Jin-i/author-R6UhyHNkNFGdxXyw4CHMxQ">Hwang Jin-i</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/S%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-058/poem-z3M3tPiLwUn8v8hY-DcVow">Sơn cư bách vịnh kỳ 058 - 山居百詠其五十八</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-jnvtlp5PrNS3FoOBBGt7-w">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/Thu-trung-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ngh%E1%BB%87-L%E1%BA%A1ng-S%C6%A1n-tr%E1%BA%A5n-h%E1%BA%ADu-ti%E1%BA%BFp-B%E1%BA%AFc-s%E1%BB%A9-h%C3%A0nh-gian-thu%E1%BA%ADt-ho%C3%A0i/poem-6dgMx7l5-oloA9g5Av8Ccg">Thu trung phụng nghệ Lạng Sơn trấn hậu tiếp Bắc sứ, hành gian thuật hoài - 秋中奉詣諒山鎮候接北使,行間述懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Th%E1%BB%A9-v%E1%BA%ADn-B%C3%B9i-Nh%E1%BB%8B/poem-ZLNDlUEd1OzopEskij-98w">Thứ vận Bùi Nhị - 次韻裴二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-gi%C3%A1m-th%C3%AD-S%C6%A1n-Nam-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-vi%E1%BB%87n-trung-ng%E1%BA%ABu-thu%E1%BA%ADt/poem-p8zdsgKaj4v3K1DKOePRpA">Trọng đông phụng giám thí Sơn Nam trường, viện trung ngẫu thuật - 仲冬奉監試山南場，院中偶述</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C4%83n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Kh%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BA%A5t-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%E1%BB%A7-thi%E1%BA%BFt-kho%C3%A1i-h%C3%AD-t%E1%BA%B7ng-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-ca/poem-loqXR_RH7MuCHDDme5Ig1w">Văn Hương Khương thất thiếu phủ thiết khoái hí tặng trường ca - 閿鄉姜七少府設膾，戲贈長歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/Xu%C3%A2n-trung-s%C6%A1n-am-k%E1%BB%B7-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-DUQtk-KVxUmdIVr8elvBNQ">Xuân trung sơn am kỷ sự - 春中山庵紀事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br></div>	</div>
